    {
      "type": "text", "id": "ct_label",
      "x": 70, "y": 490, "width": 380, "height": 170,
      "text": "SCT-013-030 CT (clamped on compressor hot leg)\n    TRRS SLEEVE ──┐\n                   ├─[10kΩ]──┐       bias ≈ Vref/2\n                   │           ●──────▶ A2\n            TIP ─┤         +3V3 ──[10kΩ]─┘\n                   │                  │\n                   │         10 µF ─── GND\n                   └──── GND ─────────┘\n\nBurden resistor is internal to the SCT-013-030 (0–1 V AC).",
      "originalText": "SCT-013-030 CT (clamped on compressor hot leg)\n    TRRS SLEEVE ──┐\n                   ├─[10kΩ]──┐       bias ≈ Vref/2\n                   │           ●──────▶ A2\n            TIP ─┤         +3V3 ──[10kΩ]─┘\n                   │                  │\n                   │         10 µF ─── GND\n                   └──── GND ─────────┘\n\nBurden resistor is internal to the SCT-013-030 (0–1 V AC).",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
