      "x": 910, "y": 210, "width": 340, "height": 180,
      "text": "Sensirion SDP810-125Pa (I²C)\n\n  VIO  ← +VIO  (3V3)\n  GND  ← GND\n  SDA  ↔ SDA  (pull-ups on-board)\n  SCL  ↔ SCL\n\nPorts + and − tapped across the\nfilter frame via ¼″ silicone tube.",
