      "type": "text", "id": "power_label",
      "x": 910, "y": 450, "width": 420, "height": 200,
      "text": "Power path (RTU 24VAC → 5V DC)\n\n  24VAC at RTU control bd. ──▶ AC/DC supply (5V, 2A)\n                               │\n                               ▼\n                         Mojo (inline)\n                               │\n                               ▼\n                    Notecarrier CX  +VBAT / +5V pad\n\nMojo reports cumulative mAh over its Qwiic link\nto the Notecard for ground-truth power validation.",
      "originalText": "Power path (RTU 24VAC → 5V DC)\n\n  24VAC at RTU control bd. ──▶ AC/DC supply (5V, 2A)\n                               │\n                               ▼\n                         Mojo (inline)\n                               │\n                               ▼\n                    Notecarrier CX  +VBAT / +5V pad\n\nMojo reports cumulative mAh over its Qwiic link\nto the Notecard for ground-truth power validation.",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3,
